text: A staphylotoxin can be any of these toxins produced by Staphylococcus bacteria: *Staphylococcus aureus alpha toxin *Staphylococcus aureus beta toxin *Staphylococcus aureus delta toxin *Staphylococcal Enterotoxin B *Exfoliatin *Panton-Valentine leukocidin *Toxic shock syndrome toxin
title: Staphylotoxin
